reviewText: Those who collect figure skating memorabilia should definitely consider owning this.
was expecting to see the complete finals. the rare footage though was a treat. what could  have been. recommended. ken.

The 1961 crash that killed the US Figure Skating Team was horrific, but so much came from that tragedy in the way of amazing skaters.  This is something I'll watch over and over. I saw it once on TV when the DVD first came out, and am so glad to have my own copy.
